---
title: Creamy Gnocchi and Snap Peas with a Lemon-Mint Ricotta Dollop
description: Soft, pillowy gnocchi is lightly seared in the pan then dressed in a simple cream cheese sauce. The fresh lemon-mint ricotta dollop on top adds a perfect pop of brightness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-gnocchi-and-snap-peas-4189b9dc.jpg
